--------------------------------------------------
Big Mana Crystals:
--------------------------------------------------

Constructed Mana Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Generate 1.

1: Until the End of the Turn, this Mana
Crystal becomes a Construct Creature (Str: 2, Vit: 1) with Rush.
It remains a Big Mana Crystal.

--------------------------

Collapsing Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Generate 1.

1, EXHAUST: Destroy target Big Mana Crystal an Opponent controls.
Destroy this Mana Crystal.

--------------------------

Shifting Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Search your Crystal-Collecting for a Small Mana Crystal, put it on the Battle
exhausted, then shuffle your Crystal Collection.

--------------------------

Burning Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Generate R.
RRR, EXHAUST(Slow): Deal 2 Damage to any Target.

--------------------------

Enlightening Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Generate B.
BBB, EXHAUST(Slow): Foresight 1, then draw 1 Card.

--------------------------

Restoring Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Generate G.
GGG, EXHAUST(Slow): Put target Creature Card from your Graveyard on the Top of your Spellbook.

--------------------------

Soothing Crystal:
Rarity: GOLD

EXHAUST: Generate W.
WWW, EXHAUST(Slow):
Choose one:
- Heal target Creature for 2.
- Put a Shield-Counter on target Creature.
- Summon a Knight.

--------------------------

